    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3052220/extras/45c013a8bb433e3b38d30ad12b003464.avif?t=1721570570\" width=600 height=132 /></span><br>在 Red Door Yellow Door 中，深入探索你内心的深处，起初看似普通的仪式很快揭示出其邪恶的本质。在探索怪异和令人恐怖的环境时，揭示这一神秘实践的真正本质。直面你最深的恐惧，解决复杂的谜题，并在寻找神秘的红黄门的旅程中逃避邪恶的实体。你能找到门并返回现实，还是会永远被困在黑暗中？<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3052220/extras/beea9c0aa45945c97d1dfc789b62daba.poster.avif?t=1721570570\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3052220/extras/beea9c0aa45945c97d1dfc789b62daba.webm?t=1721570570\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3052220/extras/beea9c0aa45945c97d1dfc789b62daba.mp4?t=1721570570\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3052220/extras/bf9c8646de43502822722b270e1eda94.webp?t=1721570570\" width=450 height=24 /></span><br>解决复杂的谜题，解锁新区域，揭开噩梦的秘密。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3052220/extras/f644e1e7a459169adb415262781f63aa.poster.avif?t=1721570570\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3052220/extras/f644e1e7a459169adb415262781f63aa.webm?t=1721570570\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3052220/extras/f644e1e7a459169adb415262781f63aa.mp4?t=1721570570\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3052220/extras/7259a127b9d6f9f8fde432b62524a46f.webp?t=1721570570\" width=450 height=24 /></span><br>避开并智取各种恶意实体，它们决心将你困在噩梦中。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3052220/extras/5d98d61cc8342059cb866d1c99a3fee4.poster.avif?t=1721570570\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3052220/extras/5d98d61cc8342059cb866d1c99a3fee4.webm?t=1721570570\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3052220/extras/5d98d61cc8342059cb866d1c99a3fee4.mp4?t=1721570570\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3052220/extras/b107249e7e36ebf2e02da804ba0caa63.webp?t=1721570570\" width=450 height=24 /></span><br>你越深入，世界就越展现出它扭曲而可怕的本质。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3052220/extras/f66e086857fe89b4b8cb26ffc5d47ecd.poster.avif?t=1721570570\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3052220/extras/f66e086857fe89b4b8cb26ffc5d47ecd.webm?t=1721570570\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3052220/extras/f66e086857fe89b4b8cb26ffc5d47ecd.mp4?t=1721570570\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>在《红门黄门》中，你将探索一个充满隐藏危险和潜伏在阴影中的恶意实体的诡异氛围世界。当你在这个扭曲的现实中穿行时，你需要找到钥匙并解决谜题以继续前进。每打开一扇门，你就离最终目标——找到难以捉摸的红黄门钥匙——更近一步，这将让你从无情的噩梦中醒来。<br><br>为未知之旅做好准备，每一个选择都可能是你的最后一次。这不仅仅是一个游戏，它是对你勇气和决心的考验。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3052220/extras/d958cd5c3a58e4dfe165a6148668a596.webp?t=1721570570\" width=450 height=24 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3052220/extras/558645267493f0c42368fcc3d3716858.poster.avif?t=1721570570\" width=600 height=82 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3052220/extras/558645267493f0c42368fcc3d3716858.webm?t=1721570570\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3052220/extras/558645267493f0c42368fcc3d3716858.mp4?t=1721570570\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
